{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"193225-what-will-happen","title":"¿Qué pasaría si...?","description":"¿Qué pasaría si Sunita presiona su ombligo? ¿O si estira sus orejas? Lee este tierno cuento sobre el poder de la imaginación. ","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sigo leyendo"],"illustrators":["Vivekananda Roy Ghatak"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Sigo leyendo","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/193225-what-will-happen"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/726929/size3/15b2e1748d152812ed5526070aca52ef.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/726929/size6/15b2e1748d152812ed5526070aca52ef.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88603/size6/d0c339bacb034de36210e5dd5be72294.jpg","text":"¿Qué pasaría si...","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89453/size6/009f152a63a7c4619468688a3036313f.jpg","text":"... presiono mi ombligo?","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88742/size6/0bda417ca4812326df4393109cbdb0fe.jpg","text":"¡sssss! \n¡Puedo deslizarme debajo de la puerta!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88608/size6/e716255e631cc19686239eb5e0dea1b6.jpg","text":"¿Qué pasaría si como todas estas semillas de tomate?\n¡Pum pum!\n  ¡Puedo lanzar tomates a los villanos!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88750/size6/569777fa90a773c0d4c6226c40b2057d.jpg","text":"¿Qué pasaría si aspiro \nprofundamente?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88693/size6/5ba644944100cd2c3bb47561515fa390.jpg","text":"¡Me convertí en un globo! No puedo parar de rebotar y rodar por todas partes.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89454/size6/d794fcae9f6aa3923bf53cc24d6aabb0.jpg","text":"¿Qué pasaría si cierro los ojos con mucha fuerza?\n¡Chiss!\n¡Soy Invisible! Nadie sabe que estoy aquí.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88615/size6/f05aecb42a79cebfef20a18f5c3ac98e.jpg","text":"¿Qué pasaría si estiro mis orejas?\n¡Yupiii!\nEstoy volando con los pájaros.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88662/size6/3944e42d955b74cef810a1007d6671f7.jpg","text":"¡Chiss!\nNo le cuentes a nadie sobre mis superpoderes.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88619/size6/5052786d55b35afdfb6fbcbdc194727a.jpg","text":"Algún día podré usar \n                  todos mis superpoderes.  \n                   ¡ Y salvaré el mundo!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/88741/size6/da61b0076fb3a075eda810892d48197e.jpg","text":"12/12","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":102}}